<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:171px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Windows7logo.png" class="image" title="Windows 7 logo"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a3/Windows7logo.png" width="169" height="110" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
